T1  - Organizational Logic for Concurrent Government in Metropolitan Areas
AU  - Boschken, Herman L.
Y1  - 1976/01/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1976.4408737
